---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<LegalLayout title="About TrailNestCo" description="Learn who's behind TrailNestCo, our mission, and how we test the gear we recommend." path="/about">
  <p>
    {SITE.name} is an independent media publication covering {SITE.niche.primary.toLowerCase()} —
    from camping and backpacking equipment to the everyday home essentials that make daily life easier.
    We were founded in {SITE.founded} on a simple idea: gear advice should come from people who actually
    use the products, not from whoever pays the highest commission.
  </p>

  <h2>Our mission</h2>
  <p>
    The outdoor and home-goods market is flooded with thin "best of" listicles that are never tested and
    rarely updated. {SITE.name} exists to be the opposite: a small team of editors and category specialists
    who test gear in real conditions, verify specifications against manufacturer documentation, and update
    our guides when products change or go out of stock.
  </p>

  <h2>What we cover</h2>
  <ul>
    {SITE.niche.sub.map((s) => <li>{s.label}</li>)}
  </ul>

  <h2>Our team</h2>
  <p>
    {SITE.name} is led by Editor-in-Chief <a href="/authors/james-carter">James Carter</a> and Senior Editor
    <a href="/authors/sarah-nguyen"> Sarah Nguyen</a>, supported by category specialists including
    <a href="/authors/mike-alvarez"> Mike Alvarez</a> (outdoor gear) and
    <a href="/authors/laura-bennett"> Laura Bennett</a> (home &amp; travel). Every contributor's full bio,
    expertise, and published work is listed on their author page.
  </p>

  <h2>How we make money</h2>
  <p>
    {SITE.name} is reader-supported. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a
    commission from the retailer at no additional cost to you. This revenue funds our testing and editorial
    operations. It never determines which products we recommend or how we rank them — see our
    <a href="/editorial-policy">Editorial Policy</a> and <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a>
    for the specifics.
  </p>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>
    {SITE.business.legalName}<br />
    {SITE.business.addressFull}<br />
    Phone: <a href={SITE.business.phoneHref}>{SITE.business.phone}</a><br />
    Email: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.business.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.business.contactEmail}</a>
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
